itemLabel: Susan Hussey, Baroness Hussey of North Bradley
itemDescription: Lady-in-Waiting to Queen Elizabeth II; godmother of Prince William, Duke of Cambridge

wikipedia_page.main: Susan Katharine Hussey, Baroness Hussey of North Bradley,  (née Waldegrave; born 1 May 1939) known as Lady Susan Hussey until her husband was raised to peerage in 1996, is a British noblewoman who serves as a Woman of the Bedchamber to Queen Elizabeth II.
